## EcoBadge Technology

EcoBadge is born from our commitment to sustainability, offering high-quality emblems made with up to 85% recycled materials.

### Key Features

- **Certified recycled materials** — full supply chain traceability
- **Reduced carbon footprint** — 60% fewer emissions than conventional emblems
- **Optional biodegradable** — options that decompose in 2-5 years

### Certifications

Our processes are ISO 14001 certified and our materials are verified by international sustainability organizations.
